      <title class="- topic/title ">
         <ph class="- topic/ph " props="autonumber">6.205</ph> Set-asides for HUBZone small business concerns.</title>
      <conbody class="- topic/body concept/conbody ">
         <ol id="d372e13" class="- topic/ol ">
            <li class="- topic/li ">
               <p class="- topic/p " id="d386e10">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(a)</ph>
                  To fulfill the statutory requirements relating to the HUBZone Act of 1997 (<xref href="https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=granuleid:USC-prelim-title15-section631&amp;num=0&amp;edition=prelim"
                        format="html"
                        scope="external">15 U.S.C. 631 note</xref>), contracting officers may set aside solicitations to allow only HUBZone small business concerns to compete (see <xref href="19.1305.dita#FAR_19_1305"
                        base="i1099604"
                        outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                        class="- topic/xref ">19.1305</xref>).
               </p>
            </li>
            <li class="- topic/li ">
               <p class="- topic/p " id="d386e24">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(b)</ph> No separate justification or determination and findings is required under this part to set aside a contract action for HUBZone small business concerns.</p>
            </li>
         </ol>
      </conbody>
   </concept>
